---
title: Spring boot cli
date: "2019-12-19T00:00:00.284Z"
description: "spring boot cli"
---

use sdkman to install springboot cli


sdk install springboot


spring init --build=gradle --dependencies=web,data-jpa my-project

or a groovy app
```
@RestController
class WebApplication {

    @RequestMapping("/")
    String home() {
        "Hello World!"
    }

}
```

and run spring run hello.groovy
